legs.end_address: Kültür, Atatürk Blv. No:16, 49300 Muş Merkez/Muş, Turkey
legs.start_address: Aktaş, Orta Hamam, 14200 Bolu Merkez/Bolu, Turkey

steps.html_instructions: Head northeast on İzzet Baysal Cd. toward Kocabey Sk.
Keep left to stay on Ankara Bolu Yolu/D100

Turn left onto Anadolu Otoyolu Bolu Doğu Bağlantısı
Partial toll road

Keep right at the fork and merge onto Anadolu Otoyolu/O-4/E80
Toll road

Take the exit toward Gerede-Karabük Bağlantısı/E80
Toll road

Continue onto Gerede-Karabük Bağlantısı/E80
Continue to follow E80
Partial toll road

Continue straight onto Samsun Amasya Yolu/D100/E80
Continue to follow D100/E80

Take the ramp onto Sivas Erzincan Yolu/D100/E80
Continue to follow D100/E80
Bardakçı Köyü Yolu turns slightly right and becomes Pülümür Yedisu Yolu
Pülümür Yedisu Yolu turns slightly right and becomes Derindere Köyü Yolu
Derindere Köyü Yolu turns slightly left and becomes Pülümür Yedisu Yolu

At the roundabout, take the 2nd exit onto Muş Bitlis Yolu/D300/D955
Continue to follow D300/D955

Turn right onto Atatürk Blv.
Destination will be on the left
